public abstract class VersionableRestElementResource<P extends RestResource,V extends Versionable> extends KeyableBeanRestElementResource<P,V>
Base class for non-root element resources backed by a versionable bean. The checksum for this resource is derived from the underlying bean's beanversion. Resources can extend this class directly.
